    "quantity": 0,
    "description": "[code][color=#00ffaa]In the celestial garden, among soft clouds and eternal rainbows, grows the Angelic Mango. This sacred fruit, is known for its ability to bring peace and joy to anyone who tastes it. Its soft, angelic feathers and golden aura make it a symbol of purity and hope. Legend has it that the Angelic Mango was a gift from an ancient goddess of light, who wished to spread serenity in the hearts of all living beings. Whenever a pure soul picks this fruit, an angel receives its wings, spreading love and benevolence throughout the world.[/color][/code] Rarest Special Mango",
