    "name": "Nephilim Mango",
    "quantity": 0,
    "description": "[code][color=#A335EE]In the heart of a mysterious dimension lies a unique and legendary fruit: the Nephilim Mango. This extraordinary fruit is born from the union of angelic and demonic forces, representing a perfect balance of light and darkness. According to legend, the Nephilim Mango was created during an ancient battle between good and evil when a fallen angel and an archangel joined forces to protect the equilibrium of the universe.[/color]\n\n[color=#00ffaa]The angelic half of the mango is a soft, ethereal blue, emanating a calm and serene light, accompanied by a pure, feathered wing. This side symbolizes purity, grace, and peace, exuding a divine aura that inspires all who come near. [/color]\n\n[color=#FF0000]The demonic half, on the other hand, is a deep and intense red, featuring twisted horns, a bat-like wing, and a pointed tail. This side represents temptation, power, and dark strength.[/color]\n\n[color=#A335EE]The Nephilim Mango is rare and powerful, capable of granting its bearer both celestial wisdom and infernal strength. However, anyone who dares to taste it must be ready to confront their own shadows and inner light, as the fruit does not tolerate imbalance within the soul. Those who can balance these opposing forces may access immense power, becoming guardians of cosmic equilibrium.[/color][/code] Rarest Special Mango",
